Revision history for Perl extension MIME::Lite::TT::Japanese
0.07  Wed Nov 16 21:56:13 2005
    - now use DateTime::Format::Mail instead of Mail::Date. ( Mail::Date was disappeared from CPAN. )

0.06  Sun Aug 07 23:57:21 2005
    - implement auto linefeed.
    - now Jcode is always used. no Encode.

0.05  Wed Dec 15 20:32:24 2004
    - set Japanese local-time at Date field by default.

0.04  Wed Sep 08 18:00:07 2004
	- MIME-Header encoding is now ISO-2022-JP even when over 5.8.0.
	- Jcode is also required over 5.8.0.

0.03  Sat Jul 31 15:30:49 2004
    - now use Encode when the version of perl is 5.8.0 or more instead of Jcode.
    - add MIME::Lite::TT into PREREQ_PM.
	- fix document.

0.02  Mon Jul 27 14:57:34 2004
	- add Jcode into PREREQ_PM.

0.01  Sun Jul 25 03:36:36 2004
	- original version
